// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2024-0254 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: a4e9cab4-8f27-5b3d-962f-bbd82e2ce2b4

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*debian:10*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:11*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:12*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:20.04-ESM*")
